    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a mechanically sound example of the definitive analog driver's car. At its heart is the S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally serviced to ensure precise cam timing. Power is managed via a factory 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement through every gate. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to address known chassis fatigue, and the rear trailing arm bushings (RTABs) have been upgraded for improved lateral stability. The variable M-differential lock remains tight, providing excellent traction out of corners. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with spirited road use, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are sorted, offering the linear power delivery and telepathic steering rack feedback this platform is renowned for.",
      "price": 31500.0,
